Package: rseqR
Type: Package
Title: RNA-seq data processing pipeline
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Anil", "Chalisey", , "anilchalisey@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: Anil Chalisey <anilchalisey@gmail.com>
Description: An R-based pipeline to analyse RNA-seq data. This pipeline performs
  quality control of reads, generates gene and transcript level counts, performs 
  differential analysis, and gene pathway enrichment analyses.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
SystemRequirements: Salmon, Java, FastQC, MultiQC, Cutadapt, TrimGalore!
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
